title: Week Seven Top Football Performers
text:
Week Seven Top Football Performers Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
A fantastic slate of games over the last two days means that there were some excellent individual performances. This includes game winning touchdowns, big play rushers, tough to stop quarterbacks, and much more. Find out which players made the cut now in our top performers now!
